            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "Well, in 1803, Napoleon’s armies took from the Italians a similar statue… the Venus de Medici",
                "fr": "En 1803, l'armée de Napoléon a pris une statue similaire des mains des Italiens… la Vénus de Médicis"
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Image",
            "Parameters": {
                "Width": 615,
                "Height": 799,
                "Display": "FullScreenWidth",
                "Source": "Web",
                "Path": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dgg6oz8uy/image/upload/v1535040170/museum%20app/Venus_de_Medicis.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "Type": "Text",
            "Label": {
                "en": "And it became hugely popular among the French public",
                "fr": "Et elle est rapidement devenue populaire auprès du public français"
            }
        }
    ],
